**Professional Profile**
Nguyen Anh Tuan (Galvaron) is an aspiring Game Developer with a strong foundation in information technology, demonstrating significant project-based experience. Tuan has independently developed a diverse portfolio of games, showcasing proficiency in various game systems. This includes a role-play farming game where Tuan solo-developed intricate features such as character finite state machines, inventory, farming, trading, crafting, combat, and a comprehensive saving system. Further projects include a 2D UI-focused quiz game utilizing Unity UI and C#, and a multi-stage 2D Mario-like tile-based game complete with player mechanics, monster interaction, and state preservation.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Unity, C#, Unity UI, Tilemap System, Game Mechanics, Finite State Machine (FSM), System Design, Excel, Word, Powerpoint.

**Education & Certifications**
Nguyen Anh Tuan is pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science from Ton Duc Thang University. No certifications were provided.